channel.title: Poem
channel.description:
Oh Bots, Oh bots. Now where will you run? Seems your tyranny is coming undone. Those countless times, when you have stolen my ore, and made me question what a skill cape is for. You stay online for hours on end, and seem to ignore every message I send. I'm sorry to say, but you won't be missed. Runescape is to small for us to coexist.
Found this on google and thought it was clever.
